text: "Think I Need It Too" is a 2009 song by Echo & the Bunnymen and is the leading single from their 11st studio album The Fountain. It did not chart at all in the United Kingdom of in Scotland. ==Track listing== #"Think I Need It Too (Album Version)" – 3:41 #"November (Album Version)" – 4:04 ==References== Category:2009 songs Category:Alternative rock songs Category:Echo & the Bunnymen songs
title: Think I Need It Too
